    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潜入一个感人的故事</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小男孩儿的大部分时间都在医院度过。他不知道，医院的围墙外隐藏着一个复杂而迷人的世界。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >今天是小孩儿的生日，他的妈妈不在身边。取而代之的是阴影。在阴影的唆使下，小孩儿逃出了医院，踏上了寻找妈妈的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来解开谜题，躲避敌人，结交朋友，来帮助小男孩儿回家吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真正的冒险正在等待着小孩儿啊！现在，他的命运掌握在你的手中...... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112220/extras/095729b540029107f8877832a2b5ab24.avif?t=1757519654\" width=616 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特征</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t以孩子的眼光看待熟悉的事物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t帮助男孩儿战胜疾病。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t试图躲避麻烦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t和垃圾鼠一起玩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t驯养小狗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t躲在公共厕所里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t从蜂蜜旁赶走蜜蜂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t创建一个关于你冒险的故事，并记录在你的相册中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t探索一个小镇，来揭开它的神秘面纱吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t结识阴影。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t做出艰难决定，保持明暗平衡。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >●\t了解你独特玩法的结局。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112220/extras/284960c5c924f0996dba7bc0a7c5a7c8.poster.avif?t=1757519654\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112220/extras/284960c5c924f0996dba7bc0a7c5a7c8.webm?t=1757519654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3112220/extras/284960c5c924f0996dba7bc0a7c5a7c8.mp4?t=1757519654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
